  ⋀ᶜ⁵𝟘ᶜ = flip ≈ᶜ-trans (+ᶜ-identityˡ _) $ +ᶜ-congˡ ⋀ᶜ⁴𝟘ᶜ

opaque

  -- A lemma related to some of the usage rules for J and K.

  ω·ᶜ+ᶜ²𝟘ᶜ : ω ·ᶜ (𝟘ᶜ +ᶜ 𝟘ᶜ) ≈ᶜ 𝟘ᶜ {n = n}
